When
\fBnone\fR
is used either in the
\fBSOURCE\fR
or
\fBDEST\fR
column, the rule is ignored\&.
.sp
\fBall\fR
means "All Zones", including the firewall itself\&.
\fBall\-\fR
means "All Zones, except the firewall itself"\&. When
