\fBACTION\fR
is
\fBDNAT\fR
or
\fBREDIRECT\fR\&.
.PP
Example:
.RS 4
\fBloc:192\&.168\&.1\&.3:3128\fR
specifies a local server at IP address 192\&.168\&.1\&.3 and listening on port 3128\&.
