\fBACTION\fR
is
\fBREDIRECT\fR
or
\fBREDIRECT\-\fR, this column needs only to contain the port number on the firewall that the request should be redirected to\&. That is equivalent to specifying
\fB$FW\fR::\fIport\fR\&.
.RE
