.PP
\fBORIGDEST\fR \- [\fB\-\fR|\fIaddress\fR[,\fIaddress\fR]\&.\&.\&.[\fIexclusion\fR]|\fIexclusion\fR]
.RS 4
Optional\&. If ACTION is
\fBDNAT\fR[\fB\-\fR] or
\fBREDIRECT\fR[\fB\-\fR] then if this column is included and is different from the IP address given in the
\fBDEST\fR
