\fBDNAT\-\fR
or
\fBREDIRECT\-\fR
rule\&. In this usage, the list of addresses should not begin with "!"\&.
.sp
It is also possible to specify a set of addresses then exclude part of those addresses\&. For example,
\fB192\&.168\&.1\&.0/24!192\&.168\&.1\&.16/28\fR
