\m[blue]\fBshorewall\-exclusion\fR\m[]\&\s-2\u[8]\d\s+2(5)\&.
.sp
See
\m[blue]\fBhttp://www\&.shorewall\&.net/PortKnocking\&.html\fR\m[]\&\s-2\u[13]\d\s+2
for an example of using an entry in this column with a user\-defined action rule\&.
.sp
